{"4175440": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "魯蛇穿越異世界 -做愛、打工、萬事屋-", "steam_appid": 4175440, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>正統續作，不必玩過前作也能沉浸其中。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>七位女性、七套彼此牽動的玩法系統。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>21張全動態HCG——這次的異世界，更色，也更有策略。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/a8b7408889246228ba390ba9334164e8.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本遊戲是《魯蛇穿越異世界 -征服世界前得先征服可愛妹子-》的續作，即使未曾體驗前作，也能完整享受本作內容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這次穿越，比上次更失控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你以為穿越一次就夠慘了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >錯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這次醒來，是在一個看似現代的世界，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卻早已被失控的慾望侵蝕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔素感染正在擴散。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有人變得暴躁、有人變得危險——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也有人，變得比你想像中還要渴望色色的親密接觸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，依然是那個對魔素免疫的異界魯蛇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/4ad5256292887f63abc81a7ca2275a6c.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/4ad5256292887f63abc81a7ca2275a6c.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/4ad5256292887f63abc81a7ca2275a6c.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7f8ae83d00ace43bf2c8d735c7743c93.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7f8ae83d00ace43bf2c8d735c7743c93.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7f8ae83d00ace43bf2c8d735c7743c93.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>七位獨具魅力的女主，等你征服</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守不住治安的菜鳥女警</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背負責任的白髮醫生</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被慾望包圍的OL</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愛錢到不行的送貨員</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火辣卻缺客源的健身教練</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >渴望「深入交流」的圖書館管理員</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遺失裝備的Coser</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她們都有麻煩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你接下委託，替她們解決。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至於回報——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自然是色色「互助」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/17f89c749c716b2feb6b3b669bd0b61c.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/17f89c749c716b2feb6b3b669bd0b61c.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/17f89c749c716b2feb6b3b669bd0b61c.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>結合戰略玩法的成人遊戲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵我在 3×3 九宮格戰場對峙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >站位、陣營相剋、角色等級與裝備，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >都可能改變勝負。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帶隊掃蕩失控大樓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巡邏維護城市秩序</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派遣隊友送貨賺錢</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >訓練體能提升戰力</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市會因為你的行動而改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而她們，也會因為你而動搖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/abb13efe1209590baa86fac821cc513f.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>隊伍養成與進化系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰力不只來自等級。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色可透過培養進化：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >R → SR → SSR → UR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >階級提升將帶來大幅能力成長。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >裝備也能強化與升階：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從普通裝備，進化為更高品質的強力裝備。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在醫院成功治癒的角色，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >將成為可培養的支援單位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他們可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >參與戰鬥</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >協助送貨</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分擔任務</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初期你將依賴這些單位撐起全局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >別小看他們——培養得當，同樣能成為核心戰力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/84218c434ce0c69d3c7dd1f7fa68c16d.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人力調度與任務布局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任務會越來越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要更多可調度的戰力單位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巡邏、送貨、備戰——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人手不足，就會陷入混亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收編更多成員，合理分配資源，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這才是真正的策略核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>好感度，當然有用</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幫得越多，關係越深。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當好感累積到某個程度時，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瑟瑟環節自然解鎖。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7位可攻略角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21張全動態HCG（支援服裝變化）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色皆有專屬玩法與劇情線</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入願望清單</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜歡：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 多角色成人互動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 戰略佈陣系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 內容量紮實的R18遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在就加入願望清單，發售與更新第一時間通知你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>正統續作，不必玩過前作也能沉浸其中。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>七位女性、七套彼此牽動的玩法系統。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>21張全動態HCG——這次的異世界，更色，也更有策略。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/a8b7408889246228ba390ba9334164e8.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本遊戲是《魯蛇穿越異世界 -征服世界前得先征服可愛妹子-》的續作，即使未曾體驗前作，也能完整享受本作內容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這次穿越，比上次更失控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你以為穿越一次就夠慘了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >錯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這次醒來，是在一個看似現代的世界，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卻早已被失控的慾望侵蝕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔素感染正在擴散。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有人變得暴躁、有人變得危險——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也有人，變得比你想像中還要渴望色色的親密接觸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，依然是那個對魔素免疫的異界魯蛇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/4ad5256292887f63abc81a7ca2275a6c.poster.avif?t=17750