tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/17f89c749c716b2feb6b3b669bd0b61c.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/17f89c749c716b2feb6b3b669bd0b61c.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/81bb86ef662f172ba518cd53524f0e2e.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>結合戰略玩法的成人遊戲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵我在 3×3 九宮格戰場對峙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >站位、陣營相剋、角色等級與裝備，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >都可能改變勝負。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帶隊掃蕩失控大樓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巡邏維護城市秩序</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派遣隊友送貨賺錢</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >訓練體能提升戰力</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市會因為你的行動而改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而她們，也會因為你而動搖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/abb13efe1209590baa86fac821cc513f.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>隊伍養成與進化系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰力不只來自等級。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色可透過培養進化：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >R → SR → SSR → UR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >階級提升將帶來大幅能力成長。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >裝備也能強化與升階：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從普通裝備，進化為更高品質的強力裝備。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在醫院成功治癒的角色，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >將成為可培養的支援單位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他們可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >參與戰鬥</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >協助送貨</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分擔任務</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初期你將依賴這些單位撐起全局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >別小看他們——培養得當，同樣能成為核心戰力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/84218c434ce0c69d3c7dd1f7fa68c16d.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人力調度與任務布局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任務會越來越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要更多可調度的戰力單位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巡邏、送貨、備戰——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人手不足，就會陷入混亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收編更多成員，合理分配資源，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這才是真正的策略核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/7ce3e4f5241741d58e43e0c16091bf07.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.poster.avif?t=1775050141\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.webm?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/extras/daef8124cb06f4004e6bee2dc888247c.mp4?t=1775050141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>好感度，當然有用</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幫得越多，關係越深。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當好感累積到某個程度時，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瑟瑟環節自然解鎖。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7位可攻略角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21張全動態HCG（支援服裝變化）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色皆有專屬玩法與劇情線</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入願望清單</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜歡：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 多角色成人互動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 戰略佈陣系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 內容量紮實的R18遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在就加入願望清單，發售與更新第一時間通知你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "正統續作回歸。這次穿越更加失控，在慾望蔓延的都市裡，七位風格鮮明的女主等你「深入協助」。巡邏、掃蕩、派遣與養成交織成完整戰力循環，透過3×3戰略佈陣、角色進化升階與裝備強化打造最強隊伍。好感度提升將解鎖專屬劇情與21張全動態HCG——戰鬥與親密，同樣令人上癮。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/a1417183896db1344ee9c53d69559c09ffdfe34b/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1775050141", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/349bb378d468ee6b7099306dbafff0c71392f8ae/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1775050141", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4175440/349bb378d468ee6b7099306dbafff0c71392f8ae/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1775050141", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 8 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i7<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 16 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 16 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 3 季"}}}}